<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Indigo SV — Servicio Premium de Chófer en El Salvador</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --black: #080808;
      --deep: #0d0d12;
      --card: #111118;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --indigo: #4f46e5;
      --indigo-light: #818cf8;
      --gold: #c9a96e;
      --white: #f5f4f0;
      --muted: rgba(245,244,240,0.5);
      --font-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      --font-body: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--black);
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-weight: 300;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 24px 48px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(8,8,8,0.95) 0%, transparent 100%);
      backdrop-filter: blur(0px);
      transition: backdrop-filter .4s, background .4s;
    }
    nav.scrolled {
      background: rgba(8,8,8,0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--indigo-light); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 36px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--muted); font-size: .82rem; letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none;
      transition: color .25s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--indigo);
      color: var(--white) !important;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      font-weight: 500 !important;
      letter-spacing: .08em !important;
      transition: background .25s !important;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: #4338ca !important; color: var(--white) !important; }
    .nav-burger { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
    .nav-burger span { width: 24px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--white); transition: .3s; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative; height: 100vh; min-height: 700px;
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8,8,8,0.75) 0%, rgba(8,8,8,0.3) 60%, rgba(8,8,8,0.6) 100%),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549317661-bd32c8ce0db2?w=1800&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      transform: scale(1.05);
      animation: heroZoom 12s ease-out forwards;
    }
    @keyframes heroZoom { to { transform: scale(1); } }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      padding: 0 48px;
      max-width: 680px;
      animation: fadeUp .9s .2s both;
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .25em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--indigo-light); margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow::before {
      content: ''; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--indigo-light);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
      font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -.01em;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--muted); max-width: 460px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--indigo);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 15px 32px;
      border: none; border-radius: 2px;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
      transition: background .25s, transform .2s;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #4338ca; transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 15px 32px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      border-radius: 2px;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color .25s, transform .2s;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--white); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ── BOOKING FORM ── */
    .booking-strip {
      position: relative; z-index: 10;
      background: var(--card);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 36px 48px;
    }
    .booking-tabs { display: flex; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .tab-btn {
      background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: .78rem; letter-spacing: .14em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0 0 14px 0; margin-right: 32px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
      transition: color .25s, border-color .25s;
    }
    .tab-btn.active { color: var(--white); border-bottom-color: var(--indigo); }
    .booking-form { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .form-field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; flex: 1; min-width: 160px; }
    .form-field label {
      font-size: .68rem; letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .form-field input, .form-field select {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 2px;
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: .88rem;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color .25s;
      width: 100%;
      appearance: none;
    }
    .form-field input:focus, .form-field select:focus { border-color: var(--indigo); }
    .form-field input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }
    .form-field select option { background: var(--deep); color: var(--white); }
    .booking-submit {
      background: var(--indigo);
      color: var(--white);
      border: none; border-radius: 2px;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 14px 36px; cursor: pointer;
      white-space: nowrap;
      transition: background .25s;
      align-self: flex-end;
    }
    .booking-submit:hover { background: #4338ca; }

    /* ── SECTION COMMONS ── */
    section { padding: 100px 48px; }
    .section-label {
      font-size: .68rem; letter-spacing: .22em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--indigo-light);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .section-label::before { content: ''; width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--indigo-light); }
    h2.section-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.8rem);
      font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    h2.section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
    .section-sub {
      color: var(--muted); font-size: .95rem; line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    /* ── SERVICES ── */
    .services { background: var(--deep); }
    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 1px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .service-card {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 40px 36px;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background .3s;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .service-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px; background: var(--indigo);
      transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
      transition: transform .35s ease;
    }
    .service-card:hover { background: #14141c; }
    .service-card:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }
    .service-icon {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .service-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .service-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .88rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .service-link {
      font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .14em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--indigo-light); text-decoration: none;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      transition: gap .25s;
    }
    .service-link:hover { gap: 14px; }
    .service-link::after { content: '→'; }

    /* ── STATS ── */
    .stats {
      background: var(--black);
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 72px 48px;
      gap: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .stat {
      flex: 1; min-width: 180px;
      padding: 32px 40px;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .stat-number {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--gold);
      display: block;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .stat-label { font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }

    /* ── WHY US ── */
    .why { background: var(--deep); }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; }
    .why-left {
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621787082834-f3c2e07be4e9?w=900&q=80') center/cover;
      min-height: 520px;
    }
    .why-left::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8,8,8,0.6), rgba(79,70,229,0.15));
    }
    .why-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
    .why-item {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 36px 40px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background .3s;
    }
    .why-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .why-item:hover { background: #14141c; }
    .why-item-num {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: .85rem; color: var(--indigo-light);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .why-item h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .why-item p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .87rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ── ROUTES ── */
    .routes { background: var(--black); }
    .routes-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; }
    .route-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 2px;
      padding: 24px 28px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
      cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color .25s, background .25s;
    }
    .route-card:hover { border-color: var(--indigo); background: #14141c; }
    .route-cities {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--white);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    }
    .route-cities span { color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; }
    .route-meta { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: .08em; }

    /* ── CTA BAND ── */
    .cta-band {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1b4b 0%, #0d0d12 60%);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(79,70,229,0.3);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(79,70,229,0.3);
      padding: 80px 48px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .cta-band h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 300; max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .cta-band h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--deep);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 72px 48px 40px;
    }
    .footer-top {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 48px; margin-bottom: 64px;
    }
    .footer-brand h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .footer-brand h3 span { color: var(--indigo-light); }
    .footer-brand p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .88rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .footer-social { display: flex; gap: 12px; }
    .social-btn {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: .8rem; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color .25s, color .25s;
    }
    .social-btn:hover { border-color: var(--indigo-light); color: var(--indigo-light); }
    .footer-col h4 {
      font-size: .7rem; letter-spacing: .18em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .footer-col a {
      color: rgba(245,244,240,0.65); font-size: .88rem; text-decoration: none;
      transition: color .25s;
    }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--white); }
    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 28px;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px;
    }
    .footer-bottom p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .78rem; }
    .footer-bottom-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
    .footer-bottom-links a { color: var(--muted); font-size: .78rem; text-decoration: none; transition: color .25s; }
    .footer-bottom-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }

    /* ── WHATSAPP FLOAT ── */
    .wa-float {
      position: fixed; bottom: 28px; right: 28px; z-index: 200;
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      background: #25d366;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(37,211,102,0.4);
      animation: pulse 2.5s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(37,211,102,0.4); }
      50%       { box-shadow: 0 4px 36px rgba(37,211,102,0.7); }
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { padding: 20px 24px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .nav-links.open {
        display: flex; flex-direction: column;
        position: fixed; inset: 0; top: 64px;
        background: rgba(8,8,8,0.97);
        padding: 40px 24px; gap: 28px;
        z-index: 99;
      }
      .nav-burger { display: flex; }
      .hero-content { padding: 0 24px; }
      section { padding: 72px 24px; }
      .booking-strip { padding: 28px 24px; }
      .booking-form { flex-direction: column; }
      .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .why-left { min-height: 260px; }
      .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .cta-band { padding: 60px 24px; }
      .stats { padding: 48px 24px; }
      .stat { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .stat:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="nav">
  <a class="nav-logo" href="#"><span>Indigo</span> SV</a>
  <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
    <a href="#servicios">Servicios</a>
    <a href="#rutas">Rutas</a>
    <a href="#nosotros">Nosotros</a>
    <a href="https://wa.me/50300000000" target="_blank" class="nav-cta">Reservar</a>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-burger" id="burger" onclick="toggleNav()">
    <span></span><span></span><span></span>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">El Salvador · Servicio Premium</div>
    <h1>El chófer <em>privado</em><br>que El Salvador merece</h1>
    <p>Traslados al aeropuerto, tours, servicios corporativos y por horas. Profesionalismo, puntualidad y discreción en cada viaje.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#reservar" class="btn-primary">Reservar ahora</a>
      <a href="#servicios" class="btn-outline">Ver servicios</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- BOOKING -->
<div class="booking-strip" id="reservar">
  <div class="booking-tabs">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="setTab(this)">Ida</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="setTab(this)">Ida y vuelta</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="setTab(this)">Por horas</button>
  </div>
  <div class="booking-form">
    <div class="form-field">
      <label>Desde</label>
      <input type="text" placeholder="Aeropuerto, hotel, dirección..." />
    </div>
    <div class="form-field">
      <label>Hasta</label>
      <input type="text" placeholder="Destino..." />
    </div>
    <div class="form-field" style="max-width:160px">
      <label>Fecha</label>
      <input type="date" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-field" style="max-width:120px">
      <label>Hora</label>
      <input type="time" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-field" style="max-width:130px">
      <label>Pasajeros</label>
      <select>
        <option>1 pasajero</option>
        <option>2 pasajeros</option>
        <option>3 pasajeros</option>
        <option>4+ pasajeros</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <button class="booking-submit" onclick="submitBooking()">Buscar →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat"><span class="stat-number">5★</span><span class="stat-label">Calificación promedio</span></div>
  <div class="stat"><span class="stat-number">8+</span><span class="stat-label">Años de experiencia</span></div>
  <div class="stat"><span class="stat-number">24/7</span><span class="stat-label">Disponibilidad</span></div>
  <div class="stat"><span class="stat-number">100%</span><span class="stat-label">Precio fijo garantizado</span></div>
</div>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section class="services" id="servicios">
  <div class="section-label">Lo que ofrecemos</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Nuestros <em>servicios</em></h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Cada trayecto es diseñado para ofrecerle comodidad, puntualidad y la más alta calidad de servicio en El Salvador.</p>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">✈</div>
      <h3>Traslados al aeropuerto</h3>
      <p>Seguimiento de vuelos en tiempo real. Su chófer estará esperando sin importar retrasos. Comodidad desde la puerta de llegadas.</p>
      <a class="service-link" href="#reservar">Reservar</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">🏙</div>
      <h3>Tours por El Salvador</h3>
      <p>Volcanes, playas, pueblos coloniales y más. Descubra El Salvador a bordo de un vehículo premium con chófer privado y conocedor.</p>
      <a class="service-link" href="#reservar">Reservar</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">💼</div>
      <h3>Servicio corporativo</h3>
      <p>Transporte ejecutivo para reuniones, conferencias y viajes de negocios. Discreción y profesionalismo garantizados.</p>
      <a class="service-link" href="#reservar">Reservar</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">⏱</div>
      <h3>Alquiler por horas</h3>
      <p>Reserve su chófer por 2, 4, 6 u 8 horas. Ideal para diligencias, compras o cuando simplemente necesita total flexibilidad.</p>
      <a class="service-link" href="#reservar">Reservar</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY US -->
<section class="why" id="nosotros">
  <div class="section-label">Por qué elegirnos</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">La <em>diferencia</em> Indigo</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">No somos un taxi. Somos su socio de transporte premium en El Salvador.</p>
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-left"></div>
    <div class="why-right">
      <div class="why-item">
